body:
This PR
- renames the vertical diffusion keyword in the single column model so that it allows for adding separate `sgs` and `turbconv` later on (closes #243 #235), Ekman layer test has been verified;
- adds the  vertical diffusion keyword in the 3d and 2d nonhydrostatic mode; unit tests for this new keyword have been added, but no working experiment is running with it; a minimal working example will be added when @LenkaNovak and I work on a simple coupler case;
- fix a bug (closes #247).
